*Navigation Flow:*  
`MainActivity` → (Background Thread) → `TourListFragment` (RecyclerView) → (Item click) → `DetailActivity` (via Intent).  
Pengaturan kategori berada di `SharedPreferences`; perubahan langsung memicu reload data di fragment.

